\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>As darkness crept over the forest, Marcus discovered just how well his racial darkvision worked, which was to say very well indeed. Apparently his eyes were very well adapted to gathering what light was available and focusing it in a way that made it easy for him to distinguish shapes and movements. Which was a very good thing when he heard the rustling of a large animal moving through the undergrowth, allowing him to quickly spot the approaching trouble. Trouble that was shaped like an even larger honey badger than the one he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d slain earlier. <!$Scr_Ps::0>}
