\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus spent another hour in meditation to refill his mana and stamina pools, before standing up and stretching. He decided that yesterday\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s overly cautious approach wasn\u8217\'92t what he needed. He needed to increase his efforts to explore and find the secrets and legacies hidden in the Tutorial as well as the Dungeons it had made reference to. He had four days to complete a Dungeon, kill 98 more beasts and earn 95,800 IP if he wanted to complete all the weekly objectives he was sure were doable. Finishing in the top 100 scores for the week was really out of his hands after all, it would either happen or it wouldn\u8217\'92t while he worked on more concrete goals.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He spread his senses out once more, sweeping the area for any Mana concentrations that might lead him to something interesting. The improvements in his Mana Control skill had a massive impact on his ability to sense Mana, stretching his senses out to more than a 100 meter radius around him. Marcus oriented himself back in the direction he had been traveling yesterday and began moving purposefully while searching for treasures.}
